data.description:
! U N I C O R N ! A L E R T !
Coming soon! (A few weeks out, we are still getting it cleaned up and ready to go) 
This 4 bed, 2 bath, 1 car garage home with a finished basement is in the process of getting a light make over, it will have new paint, new roof, new doors, flooring and vinyl windows...with a large lot, mature trees and a POOL with a custom pool deck, the back yard has a ton of entertaining space...A wood burning stove in the basement helps keep the entire home warm.. a large laundry room...security system. 3 beds up, 1 bed down. This place is going to be CUTE!
